                  MORRISON
               <interp inst="t18290219-160-person1504" type="surname" value="MORRISON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290219-160-person1504" type="given" value="WALTER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290219-160-person1504" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep the Regalia, Augusta-street, Regent's-park. On the 31st of December, French and the prisoner came to my house - I changed this 5l. note, (looking at it) - I put French's name on it at the time, as I knew him; I saw him hand the change over to<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182902190068"></xptr>the prisoner - I saw him lay out 28s. with the pedlar - it is a Farnham note, No. 1787, dated the 1st of February, 1828.</p>
               <p>
            
