                  </persName>
            . I am one of the firm of the Farnham Bank. We never issue two notes of the same number, date, and amount; these are notes of our house, and were in circulation at the time.</p>
               <p>ASCOTT NORTHEY. Here is the cloth and fustian which I sold to the prisoner.</p>
